title: "Qualcomm Shares Gain on News it Will Supply 5G Modems for Apple iPhones Into 2026"
text: "Qualcomm (QCOM) shares gained more than 4% by midday Monday after the chipmaker said it would continue to provide 5G modems for Apple (AAPL) smartphones through 2026 as the iPhone maker pushes back plans for in-house production."

title: "Tesla stock rises on upgrade
source_name: "Tesla's (TSLA) stock is on the rise after Morgan Stanley upgraded the shares to ""Buy"" from ""Hold."" Morgan Stanley analyst Adam Jonas also raised his price target on the stock from $200 to $400."

title: "Tesla Call Traders Got in Ahead of Morgan Stanley Bull Note"
